<div class="bg-black rounded-lg m-10 flex-1 w-full max-w-3/4 flex flex-col items-center justify-center border-2 border-primary/50">
    <div class="relative w-full h-12 bg-zinc-800/50 rounded-t-lg flex flex-row items-center justify-center">
        <p>internet@catterm: ~</p>

        <div class="absolute right-4 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 flex flex-row items-center justify-center gap-2">
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-red-500"></div>
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-yellow-500"></div>
            <div class="w-3 h-3 rounded-full bg-green-500"></div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="w-full grow scroll-auto text-primary p-4 font-mono text-sm">
        <p>Catterm v1.0.0 - By a random internet cat (me)</p>
        <br />
        <p>Hello stranger! If you're here you are probably wondering what this is all about.</p>
        <p>In reality I was thinking on doing some simple paragraphs with things about me, </p>
        <p>but ended up realizing that would be kind of boring...</p>
        <br />

        <p>So I thought, why not make it look like a terminal? And here we are!</p>
        <p>I promise there are no hidden gems here :)</p>
        <br />

        <p>To start, try typing a command. If you need help, type "help" and press Enter.</p>
        <span class="flex flex-row items-center gap-2 h-6">
            <p class="text-center leading-6 m-0">internet@catterm: ~$</p>
            <p class="text-secondary"></p>
            <div class="w-2 h-6 bg-primary animate-pulse"></div>
        </span>
    </div>
</div>
